9#include "ipf.h"
10
11
12void
13printdstlistpolicy(policy)
14 ippool_policy_t policy;
15{
16 switch (policy)
17 {
18 case IPLDP_NONE :
19 PRINTF("none");
20 break;
21 case IPLDP_ROUNDROBIN :
22 PRINTF("round-robin");
23 break;
24 case IPLDP_CONNECTION :
25 PRINTF("weighting connection");
26 break;
27 case IPLDP_RANDOM :
28 PRINTF("random");
29 break;
30 default :
31 break;
32 }
33}
